data.description: Gorgeous 4 bed/3 bath home, centrally located! Granite countertops, crown molding, beautiful exposed beams, incredible built-ins, brick fireplace...the list goes on and on! Not to mention brand new carpets AND the A/C and hot water heater are both approximately a year old. Don't miss the dazzling pool in the backyard to keep you cool on hot summer days! Come see it today!
data.whatILove: Great neighborhood and very family friendly!  Great location to a park and retail shopping!
